### ============================================================================
### LIST AND GET
### ============================================================================

### List all zones
GET http://localhost:3000/api/zones

### Get a zone by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/zones/1

### ============================================================================
### SEARCHS
### ============================================================================

### Search zone by name (default)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/zones/search?q=Central

### Search zone by name - explicit
GET http://localhost:3000/api/zones/search?q=Norte&by=name

### Search for the zone that IS headquarters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/zones/search?q=true&by=headquarters

### Search for zones that are NOT headquarters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/zones/search?q=false&by=headquarters

### ============================================================================
### CRUD
### ============================================================================

### Create new zone
POST http://localhost:3000/api/zones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Zona Norte",
  "isHeadquarters": false
}

### Create zone as headquarters
POST http://localhost:3000/api/zones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sede Central",
  "isHeadquarters": true
}

### Update zone name
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/zones/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Zona Cntro"
}

### Set zone as headquarters
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/zones/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isHeadquarters": false
}

### Delete a zone
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/zones/1